div.div: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken 2nd Season Part 2
The second cour of Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken 2nd Season.
Akuyaku Reijou nano de Last Boss wo Kattemimashita

When Aileen, the Duke’s daughter, regains her memories of her past life, she realizes she’s barreling toward ruin at full speed. Searching for any way out of her hopeless situation, the method she chooses is to capture the heart of the last boss--the Demon Lord Claude!
(Source: Yen Press)
Mushoku no Eiyuu: Betsu ni Skill nanka Ira Nakkatan Daga

"Classes" are given at the age of 10, and the presence or absence of "skills" greatly affect life. Arel, the son of "Sword Princess" Fara and "Magic King" Leon, has been branded as "Classless"... But even without a job or skills, Arel believes he can persevere through effort.
(Source: Earth Star Entertainment, translated)

What do you do when your favorite game shuts down? Momonga decided to stay logged in right up until the very end. But when the servers go dark, he finds himself transported into the game world--and he's been transformed into his skeletal avatar from the game, awesome magical powers included! But what if he's the villain of his own story? (Source: Yen Press)
